ng (Thương hải hoành lưu) - 滿江紅（滄海横流）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-M%E1%BA%A1t-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/author-QwHGtxwbcIXnt9ZJeL8mXw">Quách Mạt Nhược</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-nguy%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF-Ti%C3%AAn-nguy%C3%AAn-hoa-th%E1%BA%A3o-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ph%E1%BB%93n-x%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-DdNo_vGUhpsV3Njs6JgWDA">Phụng hoạ nguyên nhật ứng chế (Tiên nguyên hoa thảo nhật phồn xương) - 奉和元日應制（仙源花草日繁昌）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-th%E1%BB%ABa-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-LHzRT_2tYsZxedOAYTvWlg">Phụng tặng Vi tả thừa trượng nhị thập nhị vận - 奉贈韋左丞丈二十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%BD-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-zGeYBMU8oPx00r2_9SPKAA">Tặng Lý thập ngũ trượng biệt - 贈李十五丈別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-20/poem-t3LIxKOyDWXx0QWMW5vdlg">Tần Châu tạp thi kỳ 20 - 秦州雜詩其二十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
